Features:

 * GWM/sharpshooter
 * Spells w/DC (just roll damage)
 * Other actions requiring rolls (grapple, push, shove, tumble, etc)
 * List standard actions, but no rolls (dodge, disengage, dash)
 * General character info (level, abilities, skills, prof)

